## üìä VISUAL SYSTEM PRINCIPLES

### Consistency
- Same logo everywhere (no modifications, variations only as documented)
- Color palette used consistently across all touchpoints
- Typography hierarchy maintained
- Spacing/sizing rules followed

### Flexibility
- Logo works in color, monochrome, inverted
- Scales from 0.5" to 48" without loss of quality
- Works on white, colored, and photographic backgrounds
- Stacks and locks up for various orientations

### Scalability
- All assets delivered in vector format (AI, SVG)
- High-res raster exports included (PNG, JPG at 300 DPI)
- Icon system buildable and extensible
- Secondary marks don't require permanent licensing

### Professional
- Suitable for Fortune 500 pitches
- Credible for nonprofit grant applications
- Appropriate for academic partnerships
- Professional enough for industry conferences

